Description:
Felt letter boards, sometimes called menu boards, have been around for decades.  Growing up you probably took for granted that they were in places you went every single day like schools, churches, offices, restaurants, and waiting rooms. Letter boards have always been basic and built to convey important information.  RIVI has revived the traditional letter board for today's home!  They are simple and functional but also have a great modern minimalist design style.  The style is minimalist but has maximum design possibilities. They are perfect for personalizing your space and refreshing them whenever you feel up to a new message or inspiration.
RIVI felt letter boards are available to you with oak frames to fit the space you dream to display it in your home or office.  They come with generous 290 character letter set in Helvetica font and 3/4" size so you can create any message your heart desires.  The possibilities are endless!

Product name: Play Canopy - White - Hanging Play Tent
Description:
Item is made to order. Please allow two weeks from purchase date until your item will ship. 
This tent is made with a very lightweight cotton gauze fabric.
It is still strong and durable but is very thin and let's the light through so beautifully. It's the same type of fabric that some receiving blankets you may have seen or used are made from. I have added a little loop that hangs down on the inside of the tent so you could hang a little something on the inside like the paper ball or pompom. They even make lanterns with a battery operated light that I think would be so cute to add a little light on the inside!  It is very gender neutral and would be perfect for a boy, girl, or shared space. This tent is one that could really grow with your child as their room decor and tastes change because it has such a simple timeless design. 
The inside of this tent has a custom made hoop that is included with your order. It is 20" across. The tent hangs about 8 feet long and gradually gets larger towards the bottom. 
All products designed by me, Terri. 
This tent is all about letting your Imagination take over! My kids like to pretend all different things in their tent. It is the perfect little hideaway from toddler to teen. Add a book sling (also available in my shop) on the wall next to it and let it be a reading nook.
All of the inside seams are serged to prevent fraying and give everything a very professional look inside and out.  It is very simple to put together, all you need is the included hoop, a hook and chain or rope to hang and adjust it to your liking.
To wash your tent wash in cold water with mild detergent on gentle cycle, tumble dry low and remove just before dry.

Product name: Custom upcycled REWORKED vintage BOHO boots festival BOOTS gypsy boots ankle boots belted boots Cowgirl Boots Upcycled boots
Description:
Hello and welcome to my boot design shop where I can make your design come to life! I am the original boot remaker here on Etsy since 2012! Please read on to see everything about the design process from ordering to my creating your vision!!! 
*THE HEEL OF THIS BOOT CAN BE 1.5 INCH - 3 INCH unless you specify. It can take longer to get the higher heeled boots.
CUSTOM ORDER: (Photos in the listing are representations of boots I have made in the past and not the actual boots you will receive). This is a design process that takes time and each pair is an original.
The process of a custom design:
1) You place order and pay, and on your order comments, you can tell me style preferences.
2) After about 3 weeks, I message you in Etsy with photos of your boots for you to approve of or request any desired changes. It is important you check Etsy for your messages from me.
3) If no changes are needed, I complete the boot attachments and ship your boots in about 1-2 days.
4) If changes are requested, I will send out new photos in a few days and then ship upon your approval. 
What you will get:
You will receive from me one pair of boots (as photos I have sent you show) made of leather in the color, style, and size you have requested with permanently attached decoration. Your boots may be vintage (preowned) or sometimes new leather boots.  If you require new boots, you may use the order listing for NEW boots in my shop. You will also receive insoles if the boots I used are vintage.
Refunds/Exchanges: Exchange only on custom orders (no refunds). See my shop policy.
To see my past work:  https://www.pinterest.com/julielikesart/thelookfactory/
*Special Notes:  I have made hundreds of pairs - each pair original. 
Your special boots will be made to order in a similar look as listing and with leather boots in your size depending on your own style preferences. I can use belts, shells, trims, chains, charms, feathers, lace, fabrics, tapestries, and faux or vintage fur pieces – just let me know if there is something specific you like or do not like.
*Processing time: Minor delays may occur if you want changes after seeing the photos or if I am backed up in orders.
*Shipping: normally 2-3 days in the US (15), and 10-15 days international (45). Express shipping available for additional fee of 20. International buyers pay their own custom duty fees if imposed.
* Sizing: I use US sizing. If you are an international customer you can use a size conversion guide such as is found here: http://www.i18nguy.com/l10n/shoes.html and I usually size up 1/2 size if using vintage as they run small. 
If you have any questions, just ask. I would love to make some special boots for you!
